'''Stonesnake''' is a recurring background character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by an unidentified extra and debuts in &quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]].&quot; Stonesnake is a member of the [[Night's Watch]], a Ranger serving under [[Qhorin Halfhand]]. He is killed by [[Free Folk|wildlings]] while scouting the [[Skirling Pass]].
